## ğŸ”„ Project Workflow

| Stage | Key Actions & Outputs |
|-------|-----------------------|
| **1. Data Cleaning** | Filled missing `TotalCharges` (tenure = 0) â†’ 0, cast to numeric, mapped `SeniorCitizen` (0/1 â†’ No/Yes) |
| **2. Exploratory Data Analysis** | Overall churn rate = **26%**. Senior citizens churn **8 pp** more. Highest churn in month-to-month contracts and electronic check users. Tenure â‰¤ 3 months is a high-risk segment. |
| **3. Pre-processing** | One-hot encoding, scaling numeric features, train/test split (80/20) |
| **4. Modeling** | Built models: Logistic Regression, Random Forest, XGBoost |
| **5. Evaluation** | Metrics: Accuracy, ROC-AUC, Precision, Recall, F1 Score |
| **6. Model Explainability** | SHAP values revealed key drivers: contract type, tenure, service usage |

